    "Wildfire risk management AI analyzes wildfire occurrences in Mediterranean landscapes, identifying climate as the primary driver.",
    "Integrated with decision support systems, it aids forest managers in fire prevention and management.",
    "Post-disaster damage assessment AI-driven Ultra-High-Resolution Aerial (UHRA) imagery and transformer models achieve 88% accuracy in multi-class damage predictions, enhancing post-disaster assessments.",
